Once $ETH breaks out this 7-year long consolidation triangle against #BTC, it will be unstoppable. (In reference, the same with $XRP 7-year consolidation)

Right now, #Ethereum has to make 0.055 against #Bitcoin, we are still on track to this happening by Jan 2025

At $130k BTC,
0.055 ETH/BTC = $7,150 ETH
0.076 ETH/BTC = $9,980 ETH
0.085 ETH/BTC = $11,050 ETH
0.105 ETH/BTC = $13,650 ETH

give it time, don't fade ETH.
